    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   《魔法之境》的故事开始于一座坐落于危险的迷雾森林之中的小镇，小镇中发生了一连串神秘事件，这些事件一步步推动主角在机缘巧合下逼近小镇深藏的真相.........</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色立绘</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183450/extras/c5ff5e423294fc7c74a5375032c4ec38.avif?t=1772185490\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183450/extras_big/c5ff5e423294fc7c74a5375032c4ec38.avif?t=1772185490 width=800 height=344 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    本游戏在剧情之外还设置了不同的关卡来供玩家体验，战斗为2D弹球玩法玩家可以通过药水与技能的不同搭配来更好的击败怪物。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183450/extras/35e8cfc92d75f2dfd9dc458d432dc840.avif?t=1772185490\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183450/extras_big/35e8cfc92d75f2dfd9dc458d432dc840.avif?t=1772185490 width=800 height=448 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动作模组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   所有角色的技能以及动画都是手绘的逐帧动画<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183450/extras/9220f8872c0688df71e48331d689f7c5.avif?t=1772185490\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183450/extras_big/9220f8872c0688df71e48331d689f7c5.avif?t=1772185490 width=800 height=274 /></span></p>",
